# CyStack

### Installation
`pip install CyStack`

## CyStack: Iterator
FILO Data Structure
- push: adds a value to the stack
- pop: removes and returns the newest value
- Implements:
    - `__init__`: Takes any iterable
    - `__iter__`: Iterator
    - `__len__`: Size
    - `__str__`: String

## CyQueue: Iterator
FIFO Data Structure
- push: adds a value to the queue
- pop: removes and returns the oldest value 
- Implements:
    - `__init__`: Takes any iterable
    - `__iter__`: Iterator
    - `__len__`: Size
    - `__str__`: String
